  "title": "FOOT REFLEXOLOGIST",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Explain services to the customers</li><li>Apply pressure with the thumb and fingers to the client's feet</li><li>Communicating with guests during massages to adjust massage techniques as required.</li><li>Cleaning and sanitizing work areas.</li><li>Keep service records</li><li>Enquiring about guests' medical conditions and allergies before providing services.</li><li>Uphold hygiene standards and follow health and safety regulations</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience working as FOOT REFLEXOLOGIST.</li><li>Effective communication skills.</li><li>Exceptional customer service skills.</li><li>Patience and respect.</li><li>Able to work on weekend and public holiday</li></ul>",
